7760.quoteText:
AGE RESTRICTIONS

Although our website is a general audience site, we restrict the use of our Services to individuals age 18 and above.
7760.title: This service is only available to users of a certain age

tosdr.case: This service is only available to users over a certain age

7761.quoteText: We do not respond to do not track signals set by your browser at this time.
7761.title: This service ignores the Do Not Track (DNT) header and tracks users anyway even if they set this header.

tosdr.case: Do Not Track (DNT) headers are ignored and you are tracked anyway even if you set this header.
